data.description: UPDATED 2 bedroom, 2 bath condo on first floor level. Front courtyard. Living room with rustic fireplace. The kitchen features a granite counters, a breakfast bar, white cabinets and SS refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave and range. Both bedrooms with mirrored closet doors. New interior paint and carpet thru out. Located near shopping and restaurants. MOVE IN TODAY!
